0.  Definitions
    ------------
    “Repository” means the Lux Network genesis GitHub repository, including all
    files it contains.
    “Software” means every source‑code file in the Repository **except**
    Genesis Data.
    “Genesis Data” means the historical Lux Network blockchain state, snapshot,
    block history, chain parameters, configuration files, and any artefacts
    located under directories such as */genesis/* or */chain‑data/* that
    represent Lux.Network ledger activity from **1 Jan 2023 – 31 Dec 2024**.

